      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't feel temporary though. it feels permanent. like the color has just been drained out of everything. i look at his side of the bed and it's like there's just a hole in the world. i don't see how anyone is supposed to just \"keep going\" when the person who made everything make sense is gone. it's just exhausting.",
